2
00:01:06,817 --> 00:01:07,943
Lantas kenapa?

3
00:01:09,236 --> 00:01:11,363
Jika bukan karena aku melewati batas,

4
00:01:11,447 --> 00:01:13,574
kenapa kau semarah itu?

5
00:01:21,290 --> 00:01:22,458
Sepuluh detik.

6
00:01:25,336 --> 00:01:26,629
Sembilan detik.

7
00:01:33,219 --> 00:01:34,887
Aku takut aku yang akan melewati batas.

8
00:02:04,542 --> 00:02:07,878
Jadi, maksudmu…

9
00:02:09,338 --> 00:02:12,508
kau ingin melewati batas denganku?

10
00:02:12,591 --> 00:02:13,717
Tidak.

11
00:02:14,885 --> 00:02:17,805
Maksudku, aku tak akan melewati batas

12
00:02:18,848 --> 00:02:19,849
denganmu.

13
00:02:22,226 --> 00:02:25,521
Astaga, cara bicara
orang Seoul sungguh aneh.

14
00:02:28,607 --> 00:02:30,651
Kenapa kau tak mau melewati batas

15
00:02:32,194 --> 00:02:33,279
denganku?

16
00:02:57,928 --> 00:02:58,804
Halo?

17
00:02:59,513 --> 00:03:01,807
Aku di depan rumah. Keluarlah sebentar.

18
00:03:05,102 --> 00:03:06,979
Kenapa kau tak balas pesanku?

19
00:03:10,024 --> 00:03:13,110
Aku jadi makin merindukanmu.

20
00:03:13,193 --> 00:03:15,988
Bagaimana kau tahu alamatku?

21
00:03:16,780 --> 00:03:18,449
Jangan lakukan ini lagi.

22
00:03:19,783 --> 00:03:21,744
Atau aku akan lapor polisi.

23
00:03:22,328 --> 00:03:23,203
Lapor polisi?

24
00:03:25,164 --> 00:03:26,248
Namun…

25
00:03:28,250 --> 00:03:29,209
kaulah

26
00:03:30,711 --> 00:03:33,047
yang pertama merayuku, bukan?

27
00:03:34,340 --> 00:03:36,133
Katamu kau suka aku.

28
00:03:36,216 --> 00:03:37,927
Katamu,

29
00:03:38,469 --> 00:03:42,473
kau suka pria perhatian sepertiku!

30
00:03:43,098 --> 00:03:43,974
Bu Yoon!

31
00:03:50,105 --> 00:03:53,984
Aku membuat dua janji untuk diri sendiri
saat datang ke Shinsu.

32
00:03:55,319 --> 00:03:56,487
Pertama,

33
00:03:57,071 --> 00:04:00,824
"Aku tak akan terlibat
dengan orang tua siswa lagi."

34
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:02,701
Kedua,

35
00:04:03,285 --> 00:04:07,247
"Aku tak akan pernah terlibat
dengan orang tua siswa."

36
00:04:09,291 --> 00:04:10,167
Jadi,

37
00:04:11,293 --> 00:04:14,588
kita berdua tak bisa berhubungan
karena aku orang tua siswa?

38
00:04:15,381 --> 00:04:16,215
Ya.

39
00:04:17,091 --> 00:04:18,258
Jika bukan?

40
00:04:19,510 --> 00:04:24,056
Jika aku bukan wali Han-gyul,
maukah kau melewati batas denganku?

41
00:04:26,225 --> 00:04:27,559
-Tidak.
-Ya.

42
00:04:28,310 --> 00:04:29,186
"Ya"?

43
00:04:30,562 --> 00:04:31,855
-Tidak.
-Ya.

44
00:04:32,731 --> 00:04:34,441
-"Ya"?
-Astaga.

45
00:04:34,525 --> 00:04:37,528
Otakku menyuruh berkata tidak,

46
00:04:38,112 --> 00:04:41,532
tetapi mulut celaka ini
terus bicara seenaknya.

47
00:04:42,366 --> 00:04:45,577
Kurasa transmisi neuronku malafungsi.

48
00:04:46,328 --> 00:04:47,246
Kutunggu saja.

49
00:04:48,831 --> 00:04:49,665
Apa?

50
00:04:50,249 --> 00:04:53,377
Han-gyul baru lulus dua tahun lagi.

51
00:04:54,169 --> 00:04:57,339
Dua tahun itu cepat.

52
00:04:57,423 --> 00:05:00,092
Dari hari ini,

53
00:05:00,968 --> 00:05:02,261
itu 620 hari lagi.

54
00:05:02,344 --> 00:05:06,932
Dalam hitungan jam, itu 14.880 jam.

55
00:05:07,016 --> 00:05:09,351
Dalam hitungan menit… Berapa menit?

56
00:05:11,311 --> 00:05:13,564
892.800 menit.

57
00:05:14,982 --> 00:05:16,275
Itu lama.

58
00:05:17,026 --> 00:05:18,444
Itu lama, tetapi…

59
00:05:18,527 --> 00:05:20,779
Itu seperti menunggu
wajib militer selesai.

60
00:05:21,363 --> 00:05:23,699
Kau pikir menunggu dua tahun itu mudah?

61
00:05:23,782 --> 00:05:24,992
Tak mudah.

62
00:05:25,951 --> 00:05:28,871
Jika kulakukan seperti biasa,

63
00:05:29,747 --> 00:05:33,042
kita akan minum kopi
dan ke bioskop bersama.

64
00:05:35,961 --> 00:05:38,047
Kita merayakan hari-hari besar,

65
00:05:38,130 --> 00:05:40,299
aku memegang tanganmu dan memelukmu.

66
00:05:42,634 --> 00:05:45,637
Namun, jika kau tak mau,
tak akan kulakukan.

67
00:05:47,264 --> 00:05:49,850
Aku telah menunggu Yoon Bom
selama 36 tahun,

68
00:05:49,933 --> 00:05:52,478
dua tahun lagi tak masalah.

69
00:05:56,023 --> 00:05:56,857
Jadi…

70
00:05:58,567 --> 00:05:59,693
percayalah kepadaku.

71
00:06:01,612 --> 00:06:04,823
Pada hari Han-gyul lulus,

72
00:06:05,616 --> 00:06:07,034
kita bertemu lagi di sini.

73
00:06:07,701 --> 00:06:10,037
Itu adalah hari Sun Jae-gyu dan Yoon Bom

74
00:06:10,662 --> 00:06:11,622
menjadi kekasih.

75
00:06:12,372 --> 00:06:13,248
Baik?

76
00:06:32,643 --> 00:06:34,228
Kau berkelahi dengan siapa?

77
00:06:34,311 --> 00:06:35,229
Angin?

78
00:06:36,313 --> 00:06:39,983
Sun Jae-gyu tak ada di sini
dan yang lain sudah pergi.

79
00:06:40,067 --> 00:06:42,528
Kenapa kau berjuang keras sendirian?

80
00:06:42,611 --> 00:06:45,823
Pria lajang bisa apa di rumah
selain bermain gim video?

81
00:06:47,366 --> 00:06:50,744
Bagaimana denganmu?
Kenapa masih di sini malam-malam?

82
00:06:50,828 --> 00:06:53,539
Sinetron di TV tak asyik lagi.

83
00:06:54,957 --> 00:06:57,292
Menonton ini langsung lebih baik.

84
00:07:02,422 --> 00:07:04,508
Terserah saja.

85
00:07:13,100 --> 00:07:14,393
Permisi.

86
00:07:15,853 --> 00:07:18,230
Kau murid baru? Ini sudah tutup.

87
00:07:18,313 --> 00:07:19,898
Halo.

88
00:07:20,399 --> 00:07:23,652
Kami baru membuka kantor di atas.
Kubawakan kue beras.

89
00:07:24,570 --> 00:07:25,988
Kantor Hukum Choi I-jun.

90
00:07:26,822 --> 00:07:30,742
Maksudmu Choi I-jun, kakak Choi Se-jin?

91
00:07:30,826 --> 00:07:32,536
Ya, benar.

92
00:07:32,619 --> 00:07:33,662
Astaga.

93
00:07:35,372 --> 00:07:36,707
Terima kasih.

94
00:07:44,047 --> 00:07:46,508
Aku Oh Seong-tae, paralegal.

95
00:07:47,509 --> 00:07:48,760
Aku Seo Hye-suk.

96
00:07:48,844 --> 00:07:50,345
-Silakan duduk.
-Baiklah.

97
00:07:50,429 --> 00:07:53,140
Konsultasi hukum ranah pidana dan perdata.

98
00:07:53,223 --> 00:07:55,684
Gugatan keluarga
dan perceraian juga boleh.

99
00:07:56,393 --> 00:07:59,563
Kalau soal cerai, dia lebih pandai darimu.

100
00:08:00,147 --> 00:08:01,481
Kau sedang apa?

101
00:08:02,399 --> 00:08:05,110
Kenapa mempermalukan aku
di depan orang asing?

102
00:08:05,903 --> 00:08:06,737
Kenapa bercerai…

103
00:08:08,071 --> 00:08:08,906
memalukan?

104
00:08:10,115 --> 00:08:11,241
Maaf?

105
00:08:12,117 --> 00:08:13,744
Sebenarnya, aku juga pernah bercerai.

106
00:08:13,827 --> 00:08:15,204
Sungguh?

107
00:08:15,871 --> 00:08:18,248
Kau begitu modis dan wangi,

108
00:08:18,332 --> 00:08:20,584
kukira kau masih lajang. Kau duda?

109
00:08:20,667 --> 00:08:24,046
Ya. Kukira kau juga masih lajang, Hye-suk.

110
00:08:24,922 --> 00:08:28,634
Astaga. Dia panggil aku Hye-suk.

111
00:08:29,259 --> 00:08:32,012
Omong-omong, kapan kau bercerai?

112
00:08:32,095 --> 00:08:33,513
Tahun 2017.

113
00:08:35,807 --> 00:08:37,559
Aku di bulan Maret 2017.

114
00:08:37,643 --> 00:08:38,560
Aku bulan Mei.

115
00:08:38,644 --> 00:08:40,020
Kesepakatan atau gugatan?

116
00:08:40,103 --> 00:08:41,438
-Gugatan.
-Aku juga.

117
00:08:43,023 --> 00:08:45,651
Astaga. Kami bercerai
dengan cara yang sama!

118
00:08:45,734 --> 00:08:47,778
Kurasa kita cocok, Hye-suk.

119
00:08:47,861 --> 00:08:48,820
Ya!

120
00:08:49,780 --> 00:08:52,783
Kue beras dari mana ini? Padat sekali.

121
00:08:53,617 --> 00:08:56,328
Tentu kue beras itu padat. Haruskah cair?

122
00:08:57,454 --> 00:08:58,413
Kau tak pulang?

123
00:08:58,497 --> 00:08:59,873
Pergilah jika kau sibuk.

124
00:08:59,957 --> 00:09:01,041
Ayo.

125
00:09:01,124 --> 00:09:03,794
Aku berbincang dengan teman.
Kau pergi saja.

126
00:09:06,672 --> 00:09:08,757
Hye-suk, apa yang kau lakukan
di akhir pekan?

127
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:11,635
Di akhir pekan,
aku biasa mencuci pakaian dan…

128
00:09:13,470 --> 00:09:14,513
Tak ada yang khusus.

129
00:09:14,596 --> 00:09:17,224
Aku masih baru, tak paham daerah ini.

130
00:09:17,307 --> 00:09:19,017
Mau kuantar berkeliling?

131
00:09:19,101 --> 00:09:21,270
Sungguh? Kau bersedia?

132
00:09:21,353 --> 00:09:22,729
Aku sangat senggang.

133
00:09:24,356 --> 00:09:27,985
Kalau begitu, aku percaya kepadamu.

134
00:09:28,568 --> 00:09:30,862
Namun, kau tak boleh menunjukkannya,

135
00:09:30,946 --> 00:09:34,449
apalagi di depan para siswa dan guru.

136
00:09:37,035 --> 00:09:38,620
Enam ratus dua puluh hari.

137
00:09:41,790 --> 00:09:43,333
Mulai hari ini,

138
00:09:43,417 --> 00:09:46,169
Yoon Bom hanyalah guru Han-gyul.

139
00:09:47,045 --> 00:09:49,756
Jangan baik dan tersenyum kepadanya.

140
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:52,384
Jangan lakukan hal pribadi untuknya, ya?

141
00:10:00,434 --> 00:10:02,811
WANITA ITU

142
00:10:15,157 --> 00:10:16,950
Kalian lihat apa?

143
00:10:18,994 --> 00:10:21,288
Cepat lihat. Itu. Lihat itu.

144
00:10:27,252 --> 00:10:28,128
Itu…

145
00:10:29,379 --> 00:10:32,674
Itu wanita yang bersamanya tempo hari.

146
00:10:33,425 --> 00:10:35,093
Jika secantik itu,

147
00:10:35,177 --> 00:10:37,512
dia pasti lahir
demi kebahagiaan umat manusia.

148
00:10:37,596 --> 00:10:39,431
Sulit dipercaya.

149
00:10:39,514 --> 00:10:43,727
Kenapa Sun Jae-gyu itu beruntung sekali,
bertemu wanita secantik itu?

150
00:10:43,810 --> 00:10:45,687
Aku tak mengerti.

151
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:56,114
Kau lihat itu, Bu Bom?

152
00:11:00,243 --> 00:11:02,871
Aku telah menunggu Yoon Bom
selama 36 tahun,

153
00:11:02,954 --> 00:11:04,915
dua tahun lagi tak masalah.

154
00:11:04,998 --> 00:11:06,375
Percayalah kepadaku.

155
00:11:08,251 --> 00:11:09,294
Itu punyaku.

156
00:11:19,930 --> 00:11:22,516
Orang tua siswa berkencan itu
bukan urusanmu.

157
00:11:22,599 --> 00:11:25,727
Sebagai pengajar yang membentuk masa depan
negeri ini, jika ada waktu senggang,

158
00:11:26,436 --> 00:11:29,731
kusarankan dipakai
untuk alat mengajar dan catatan siswa.

159
00:11:29,815 --> 00:11:30,982
Aku permisi.

160
00:11:32,150 --> 00:11:33,402
Dia bicara apa?

161
00:11:33,485 --> 00:11:34,611
Ada apa dengannya?

162
00:11:37,447 --> 00:11:40,283
Apa itu? Katanya mau menunggu dua tahun,
tetapi selingkuh?

163
00:11:40,367 --> 00:11:44,621
Atau seperti kata Bu Seo,
dia suka semua wanita cantik?

164
00:11:46,873 --> 00:11:48,333
Jika secantik itu,

165
00:11:48,417 --> 00:11:50,669
dia pasti lahir
demi kebahagiaan umat manusia.

166
00:11:59,553 --> 00:12:00,387
Yah,

167
00:12:01,304 --> 00:12:05,183
tampaknya aku lahir untuk mewakili
masa depan suram umat manusia.

168
00:12:06,935 --> 00:12:11,440
Akan kutunjukkan
yang akan terjadi di Shinsu

169
00:12:11,523 --> 00:12:14,109
saat aku ingin tebar pesona.

170
00:12:14,192 --> 00:12:16,862
Aku Yoon Bom. Bersiaplah, umat manusia.

171
00:12:18,071 --> 00:12:19,531
Rambutku kuikat saja?

172
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,994
Aku adalah dewi umat manusia.

173
00:12:52,731 --> 00:12:53,982
Bagaimana gadis itu?

174
00:12:56,109 --> 00:12:57,027
Sudah berakhir.

175
00:12:58,987 --> 00:12:59,863
Apanya?

176
00:13:02,491 --> 00:13:03,366
Sun Han-gyul.

177
00:13:05,410 --> 00:13:06,369
Apa kau…

178
00:13:08,288 --> 00:13:09,623
suka aku?

179
00:13:14,169 --> 00:13:16,463
Aku melihat video Festival Olahraga tadi.

180
00:13:17,881 --> 00:13:20,008
Kau tersenyum saat aku menang.

181
00:13:21,551 --> 00:13:23,970
Namun, aku tak mengerti.

182
00:13:25,055 --> 00:13:26,097
Kenapa tersenyum?

183
00:13:27,265 --> 00:13:30,143
Triler lebih cocok bagi kita
daripada romansa.

184
00:13:31,770 --> 00:13:32,729
Triler?

185
